Assignments
~~~~~~~~~~~
1  Create a html page to develop Login functionality (Check Ref. Image).  And also  apply styles to result message. 
		a.  Welcome message display in Green color
		b.  Invalid message display in Red color
		
2.   Create a web page to process product details using JavaScript.  Calculate total amount based on the given values.  (Refer the Image)

		a.  Take the confirmation from the user before proceeding the total calculation. 

	Hint :   If qty is more than 10  	---   give 10% discount 
				 If qty is more than 20  	---   give 15% discount 
				 If qty is more than 30  	---   give 20% discount 

3.   Create a web page to perform all math operations (Add, Sub, Multiply, Div) using JavaScript.(Check Ref. Image)

Hint :   Use event.target option 

 
4.  Create a web page to read empno, ename, job, salary from the user (use input boxes). 		
		Add the details to table by insert a new row with textbox values.   (Check Ref. Image)
		
	
5.  Create a web page to implement the following requirement :  (Check Ref. Image)

		a.  Copy data from the below url and prepare array of users objects. 
						  	https://reqres.in/api/users
							
		b.  Display the users data in table format.
		
		c. Use DOM Manipulation and DOM Table methods to create new rows and cells. 

		d.  Add "Remove" in every row so that user can remove the required user.
	
